snippet.title: Day of the Toys - Doom Mod Trailer
snippet.description:
14 levels filled with punchy weapons and the most twisted monsters to ever grace the Doom engine. Savage toys driven by an insanely woke AI have turned Silicon Valley into a war zone, and only you can locate and rescue your son before you both succumb to the "Day of the Toys". Enemies can be blasted, maimed, and even set on fire...but sometimes they still keep coming back for more!

Get it here: https://mikestoybox.net/doom-maps/
